{"word":"Tithes","slug":"tithes","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tithes</b> Paid by Abraham to Melchizedek<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=20'>Gen 14:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=7&verse=6'>Heb 7:6</a><br/> Jacob vows a tenth of all his property to God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=22'>Gen 28:22</a><br/> Mosaic laws instituting<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=33'>Lev 27:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=24'>Num 18:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=7'>Deu 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=19'>Deu 12:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=29'>Deu 14:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=26&verse=15'>Deu 26:15</a><br/> Customs relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=38'>Neh 10:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=4'>Amo 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=7&verse=9'>Heb 7:9</a><br/> Tithe of tithes for priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=26'>Num 18:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=38'>Neh 10:38</a><br/> Stored in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=39'>Neh 10:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=44'>Neh 12:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=5'>Neh 13:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=12'>Neh 13:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=12'>2Ch 31:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=10'>Mal 3:10</a><br/> Payment of, resumed in Hezekiah's reign<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=10'>2Ch 31:10</a><br/> Under Nehemiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=12'>Neh 13:12</a><br/> Withheld<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=10'>Neh 13:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=8'>Mal 3:8</a><br/> Customary in later times<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=23&verse=23'>Mat 23:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=42'>Luk 11:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=12'>Luk 18:12</a><br/> Observed by idolaters<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=5'>Amo 4:5</a><br/><a href='S:Tax'>Tax</a>"}]}